column3: Identify the number of people in the image. Describe their individual body posture and what they are doing. Also, provide a gender assessment for each person.
column4: In the image, there are two naked boys standing next to each other, engaged in a playful activity. One boy is standing on the left side of the image and the other is on the right side.
